profile:
Custom Clean is focused on providing high-quality construction cleaning service and customer satisfaction - we will do everything we can to meet your expectations. All of our services are guaranteed and come highly recommended. 

Custom home builders: We would like to join your team of professionals. Your clients will love the work we do to help you present them with the home of their dreams. You hire the best trades possible to build your homes, and we would like the opportunity to be a part of that team of excellence your company is known for! Our construction cleaning awaits you.

Homeowners: Did you just build the house of your dreams? Or renovate your existing home? Do you need a renovation cleaner to help you bring out the beauty of your work? Give us a call to get your home in brand new, move-in ready!

We cover Peterborough County, City of Kawartha Lakes, and much more! Typically a one hour radius of the city of Peterborough. Call now to book your date with the best cleaning crew you will ever find at 705-559-3260. 

We are cleaning regularly for many happy builders, companies and home owners. Our website can be viewed for more details. Customclean dot ca
